---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Homepage
bodyClass: page-home page-atmosphere page-atmosphere--vellum
heroHighlights:
  - Release the thing
  - Sharpen the signal
  - Guard the work
servicePaths:
  - title: Get the release out of limbo
    body: Turn the scattered pieces around a single, EP, album, or artist-led launch into a plan that can actually leave the cave.
    href: /services/production/
    label: Plan the release
    analyticsService: production_support
  - title: Make the project harder to ignore
    body: Tighten the bios, visuals, page copy, and project materials that tell people what this is before they invent the wrong story.
    href: /services/rates-quote/
    label: Build the materials
    analyticsService: rates_quote
  - title: Ask the rights questions early
    body: Name the ownership, credit, clearance, and contract questions before they become expensive folklore.
    href: /services/legal/
    label: Check the legal track
    analyticsService: legal_status
featuredListening:
  soundcloudUrl: "https://soundcloud.com/ethernetsky/sets/95mp3"
  title: "From the orbit: ETHERNET_SKY"
  description: "A live signal from the Musifer orbit, not a velvet-rope endorsement scheme. ETHERNET_SKY's 95mp3 set moves with grit, shimmer, and enough static to keep the room awake."
  variant: feature
  className: home-listening
  sourceLabel: Listen to 95mp3 on SoundCloud
  playerTitle: ETHERNET_SKY 95mp3 SoundCloud player
---

<div class="l-page-shell l-module-stack home-page">
  <section class="card card-impact home-hero" aria-labelledby="home-hero-heading">
    <div class="l-grid--2 home-hero__layout">
      <div class="l-module-stack">
        <h1 class="card-title display-title" id="home-hero-heading">For artists building without waiting for permission</h1>
        <p class="home-hero__lede">
          Musifer helps independent artists turn songs, rough plans, stubborn ideas, and rights questions
          into work that can move in public without losing its teeth.
        </p>
        <div class="home-action-row">
          <a class="btn"
            href="/services/"
            data-analytics-event="service_interest"
            data-analytics-service="services_hub"
            data-analytics-surface="homepage_hero">
            Find your lane
          </a>
          <a class="btn btn--secondary"
            href="/blog/"
            data-analytics-event="blog_engagement"
            data-analytics-destination="blog_hub"
            data-analytics-surface="homepage_hero">
            Read the field notes
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="home-support-note">
          No permission slips. No bloated agency ritual. Bring the almost-release,
          the stubborn draft, the cursed asset folder, and the question you keep dodging.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="home-hero__aside" aria-label="Musifer starting points">
        <img class="content-logo" src="/Images/Musifer_Logo.svg" alt="Musifer brand mark">
        <p class="home-hero__aside-copy">
          Practical creative support with a little myth in the margins and a bias toward getting the work out alive.
        </p>
        <ul class="home-value-list" role="list">
          {% for point in heroHighlights %}
          <li class="home-value-chip">{{ point }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="card home-services" aria-labelledby="home-services-heading">
    <div class="home-section-header">
      <div>
        <h2 class="card-title" id="home-services-heading">Get the work out of limbo</h2>
        <p class="home-section-copy">
          A song rarely stalls because it lacks magic. It stalls because the plan,
          copy, assets, rights questions, or next ask are tangled. Musifer untangles those.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a class="home-inline-link"
        href="/services/"
        data-analytics-event="service_interest"
        data-analytics-service="services_hub"
        data-analytics-surface="homepage_services">
        See every lane
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="l-grid--3 home-route-grid">
      {% for path in servicePaths %}
      <article class="surface-card home-route-card">
        <h3 class="card-title">{{ path.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ path.body }}</p>
        <a class="home-inline-link"
          href="{{ path.href }}"
          data-analytics-event="service_interest"
          data-analytics-service="{{ path.analyticsService }}"
          data-analytics-surface="homepage_service_paths">
          {{ path.label }}
        </a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  {% set soundcloudWrapper = featuredListening %}
  {% include "components/soundcloud-wrapper.njk" %}

  <section class="card home-blog" aria-labelledby="home-blog-heading">
    <div class="home-section-header">
      <div>
        <h2 class="card-title" id="home-blog-heading">Field notes for artists allergic to vague advice</h2>
        <p class="home-section-copy">
          The blog is where the slower thinking lives: guides, essays, and process notes
          for decisions that deserve better than panic, folklore, or somebody's thread from 2018.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a class="home-inline-link"
        href="/blog/"
        data-analytics-event="blog_engagement"
        data-analytics-destination="blog_hub"
        data-analytics-surface="homepage_blog">
        Raid the library
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="l-grid--3 home-route-grid">
      {% for bucket in blog.publicBuckets %}
      <article class="surface-card home-route-card">
        <h3 class="card-title">{{ bucket.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ bucket.landingSummary }}</p>
        <a class="home-inline-link"
          href="{{ bucket.url }}"
          data-analytics-event="blog_engagement"
          data-analytics-bucket="{{ bucket.title }}"
          data-analytics-surface="homepage_blog_paths">
          {{ bucket.ctaLabel }}
        </a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="card card-impact home-final-cta" aria-labelledby="home-final-heading">
    <div class="l-grid--2 home-final-cta__layout">
      <div>
        <h2 class="card-title" id="home-final-heading">Stop circling the gate</h2>
        <p class="home-section-copy">
          Show Musifer what you are making, what keeps snagging, and where the next move needs teeth.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="home-cta-cluster">
        <a class="btn"
          href="/services/rates-quote/"
          data-analytics-event="service_interest"
          data-analytics-service="rates_quote"
          data-analytics-surface="homepage_final_cta">
          Start the quote path
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn--secondary"
          href="/contact/work-with-us/"
          data-analytics-contact="work_with_us"
          data-analytics-surface="homepage_final_cta">
          Send the signal
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
